sentences.sContent: Before this, she was called "the hairy angel" due to her thick bushy eyebrows and a flock of unaesthetic curly hair.
sentences.sContent_eng: Before this, she was called "the hairy angel" due to her thick bushy eyebrows and a flock of unaesthetic curly hair.
sentences.sCn: 此前，她曾被称为“毛茸茸的天使”——因为她拥有浓密的眉毛和一头毫无造型可言的卷发。
